@page "/blocked"

<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center p-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl w-full bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <div class="text-6xl mb-6">🚫</div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Service Not Available</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-6">
            We're sorry, but our service is not available in your country due to legal restrictions.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6 text-left mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Why am I seeing this?</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4">
                Online gambling is subject to different laws and regulations in different countries. 
                To comply with local laws and regulations, we restrict access from certain jurisdictions.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Restricted Countries Include:</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-400 space-y-1">
                <li>• United States, Canada</li>
                <li>• United Kingdom, France, Germany, Italy, Spain, Netherlands</li>
                <li>• Australia, New Zealand</li>
                <li>• China, Singapore, South Korea</li>
                <li>• Saudi Arabia, UAE, and other countries with gambling restrictions</li>
                <li>• Countries subject to international sanctions</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-yellow-900/30 border border-yellow-700 rounded-lg p-4 text-sm text-yellow-400 mb-6">
            ⚠️ Using a VPN to bypass geo-restrictions violates our Terms of Service and may result in account suspension and forfeiture of funds.
        </div>

        <a href="https://www.begambleaware.org" target="_blank" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 text-sm">
            Need help with gambling addiction? Visit BeGambleAware.org
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

